headline: Manhattan Associates (MANH) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Manhattan Associates (MANH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +16.96% and +3.47%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
